### My Knowing Holistically

My way of Knowing is based on Valuing, Being, Knowing and Doing. I adapt to stay true to myself.

```elixir
my_knowing_holistically_artefact = 
  my_knowing_artefact
  |> Artefact.combine(my_valuing_artefact)
  |> Artefact.combine(my_being_artefact)
  |> Artefact.combine(my_doing_artefact)
  |> Artefact.combine(my_deeper_being_artefact)
  |> Artefact.combine(my_deeper_knowing_artefact)
  |> Artefact.combine(my_deeper_doing_artefact, title: "My Knowing Holistically", 
      description: "My way of Knowing is based on Valuing, Being, Knowing and Doing. I adapt to stay true to myself.")

ArtefactKino.new(my_knowing_holistically_artefact)

```

